id isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-nio-plans-sell-its-first-hybrid-car-overseas-only-sources-say-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>坚定的巴勒斯坦继续在世界杯征程中与困难作斗争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/determined-palestine-continue-battle-odds-world-cup-quest-2024-11-04/</link><description>巴勒斯坦足球协会（PFA）主席告诉路透社，巴勒斯坦首次获得世界杯决赛圈资格突显了克服加沙冲突造成的破坏的决心。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 03:12:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/determined-palestine-continue-battle-odds-world-cup-quest-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>市场在充满事件的一周中为美国大选摊牌做好准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-04/</link><description>周一金融市场以谨慎态度开始本周，亚洲股市低迷，而美元在美国总统竞选即将结束的繁忙一周之前小幅下跌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 02:03:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>OPEC+推迟增产后油价涨幅超过1美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-rise-by-over-1-opec-output-hike-delay-2024-11-04/</link><description>油价周一延续涨势，因 OPEC+ 决定将增产计划推迟一个月而上涨逾 1 美元，同时市场为美国总统大选和中国重要会议的一周做好准备。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 00:39:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-rise-by-over-1-opec-output-hike-delay-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>法国捍卫欧盟，中国敦促欧盟提出令人满意的电动汽车贸易解决方案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-france-get-eu-arrive-palatable-ev-solution-2024-11-03/</link><description>中国敦促法国推动欧盟委员会达成欧洲和中国电动汽车行业都能接受的解决方案，而法国则表示，在推动推翻白兰地关税的过程中，欧盟不会在关键问题上让步。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 23:34:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-france-get-eu-arrive-palatable-ev-solution-2024-11-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国太阳能企业进入美国关税未触及的领域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-solar-firms-ever-nimble-go-further-afield-where-us-tariffs-dont-reach-2024-11-03/</link><description>越南的一些中资太阳能工厂正在减产并解雇工人，而老挝和印度尼西亚的新工厂也如雨后春笋般涌现。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 23:02:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-solar-firms-ever-nimble-go-further-afield-where-us-tariffs-dont-reach-2024-11-03/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报道称，随着美国大选临近，中国的军事活动有所增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-rise-chinese-military-activity-us-election-nears-2024-11-03/</link><description>台湾国防部周日表示，发现包括战斗机和轰炸机在内的 35 架中国军用飞机飞往台湾南部，准备前往太平洋进行演习，这是该部门连续第二天报告此类活动。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 06:35:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-rise-chinese-military-activity-us-election-nears-2024-11-03/</guid></item><item><title>2024年前9个月中国结婚登记量下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/marriage-registrations-china-drop-first-nine-months-2024-2024-11-03/</link><description>今年早些时候，中国公布全国出生率连续第二年下降，促使政府努力营造婚姻和生育文化。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 03:56:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/marriage-registrations-china-drop-first-nine-months-2024-2024-11-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国国务院总理李强将在上海进口博览会上发表讲话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-premier-li-qiang-speak-import-expo-shanghai-2024-11-03/</link><description>中国商务部周日表示，中国总理李强将在本周的中国国际进口博览会开幕式上发表讲话，北京方面试图表明步履蹒跚的经济是开放的。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 03:51:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-premier-li-qiang-speak-import-expo-shanghai-2024-11-03/</guid></item><item><title>格罗方德因向受制裁的中国公司运送芯片而被美国罚款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-penalizes-globalfoundries-shipping-chips-chinese-firm-2024-11-01/</link><description>美国周五表示，对总部位于纽约的全球第三大代工芯片制造商 GlobalFoundries 处以 50 万美元的罚款，原因是其未经授权向被列入黑名单的中国芯片制造商中芯国际的一家子公司运送芯片。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 18:02:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-penalizes-globalfoundries-shipping-chips-chinese-firm-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国将免签政策扩大到韩国等9个国家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expands-visa-free-policy-9-more-countries-including-south-korea-2024-11-01/</link><description>中国外交部周五表示，中国将向韩国、挪威和芬兰等另外九个国家的公民提供免签入境政策。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 13:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expands-visa-free-policy-9-more-countries-including-south-korea-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国确认欧盟代表团访问进行电动汽车关税谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-confirms-eu-delegation-visit-ev-tariff-talks-2024-11-01/</link><description>中国商务部周五证实，欧盟将派代表来华就电动汽车关税争端中的价格承诺进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 12:40:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-confirms-eu-delegation-visit-ev-tariff-talks-2024-11-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>